  "notes": [
    "This pilot study investigated the prevalence and clinical implications of reversible tactile hypoesthesia in patients with myofascial trigger points.",
    "The study found that 58.7% of patients with myofascial trigger points experienced reduction in hypoesthetic areas following trigger point injection therapy.",
    "The mechanism appears to involve inhibition of primary somatosensory cortex activity by nociceptive input from trigger points."
  ]
